# ================================================================
# CineSuggest – environment variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys
# ================================================================

# TMDB API key (required) — get one free at https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
VITE_TMDB_KEY=your_tmdb_api_key_here

# OMDb API key (optional) — for Rotten Tomatoes scores
# Get free at https://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx
VITE_OMDB_KEY=your_omdb_key_here

# ================================================================
# Vercel deployment:
# 1. Push to GitHub
# 2. Connect repo to Vercel (vercel.com/new)
# 3. Add the env vars above in Project Settings → Environment Variables
# 4. Vercel uses `npm run build` and serves `dist/` automatically
# ================================================================
